# Sovereign Stack

Do not suggest AWS, GCP, Vercel Postgres, or external managed databases.

- Hardware: Local bare-metal NVIDIA DGX Spark cluster.
- Database: PostgreSQL 16 host-native. Sovereign data never leaves physical hardware.
- Backend: FastAPI on Python 3.11+, async, strict Pydantic v2 schemas, SQLAlchemy 2.0.
- Frontend: Next.js 15+ App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui.
- Inference: Local vLLM containers serving Llama 3.3 70B FP4.
